QuestData.Title: Orders are Orders
QuestData.Description: Hmm, maybe wikket not so bad after all!$b$bOther baldskins not nice to hozen.$b$bHozen take this from bad wikkets!$b$bAll wikket loot goes to Kah Kah - Chief's orders!$b$bHere, wikket. You take it. Kah Kah will want to meet new hozen friend.$b$bHis camp south at Grookin Hill.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Alliance Orders to Chief Kah Kah at Grookin.
